WEBVTT

00:10:59.407 --> 00:11:03.650
when we encounter some information
that contradicts our beliefs.

00:11:04.555 --> 00:11:07.415
So the question I want
to leave you with is:

00:11:07.817 --> 00:11:09.967
What do you most yearn for?

00:11:10.771 --> 00:11:13.398
Do you yearn to defend your own beliefs?

00:11:14.128 --> 00:11:17.722
Or do you yearn to see the world
as clearly as you possibly can?

00:11:18.352 --> 00:11:19.503
Thank you.

00:11:19.527 --> 00:11:24.524
(Applause)